---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ConnectLinks from '../components/ConnectLinks.astro';
import { t, type Language } from '../utils/i18n';

export interface Props {
  lang?: Language;
}

const { lang = 'en' } = Astro.props;

// About page content (could be moved to a content collection in the future)
const aboutContent = {
  en: {
    intro1: `Traveler, observer, explorer of the unexpected.

I love to wander slowly, get lost in new places, and let what I encounter transform me.

This space was born from a personal need: to resist the rush of social media and give space, instead, to reflection.

I write only when the experience has had time to breathe, when it reveals something beyond the surface.

Each post is a thread in a personal map of inner and outer worlds, shaped by the people I meet, the landscapes I cross, and the quiet thoughts that last longer than the journey itself.`,
    intro2: ``
  },
  it: {
    intro1: `Viaggiatore, osservatore, esploratore dell'inatteso.

Amo vagare lentamente, perdermi in luoghi nuovi e lasciarmi cambiare da ciò che incontro.

Questo spazio nasce da un bisogno personale: resistere alla fretta dei social e dare spazio, invece, alla riflessione.

Scrivo solo quando l'esperienza ha avuto tempo di respirare, quando rivela qualcosa oltre la superficie.

Ogni post è un filo in una mappa personale di mondi interiori ed esteriori, plasmata dalle persone che incontro, dai paesaggi che attraverso, e dai pensieri silenziosi che durano più del viaggio stesso.`,
    intro2: ``
  }
};

const contentEn = aboutContent.en;
const contentIt = aboutContent.it;
---

<Layout>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-2 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <!-- English Version -->
      <div data-lang="en">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-6">
            {t('about.title', 'en')}
          </h1>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none mb-12">
          <div class="bg-warm-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-8 mb-8">
            <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 leading-relaxed text-lg whitespace-pre-line text-left max-w-prose mx-auto">
              {contentEn.intro1}
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Social Links -->
        <ConnectLinks 
          connectTitle={t('connect.title', 'en')}
          telegramLabel={t('connect.telegram', 'en')}
          channelLabel={t('connect.channel', 'en')}
          instagramLabel={t('connect.instagram', 'en')}
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Italian Version -->
      <div data-lang="it" style="display: none;">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-6">
            {t('about.title', 'it')}
          </h1>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none mb-12">
          <div class="bg-warm-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-8 mb-8">
            <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 leading-relaxed text-lg whitespace-pre-line text-left max-w-prose mx-auto">
              {contentIt.intro1}
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Social Links -->
        <ConnectLinks 
          connectTitle={t('connect.title', 'it')}
          telegramLabel={t('connect.telegram', 'it')}
          channelLabel={t('connect.channel', 'it')}
          instagramLabel={t('connect.instagram', 'it')}
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>